text: "Malibu" is a 2020 song by German singer Kim Petras. The music video was filmed during the COVID-19 lockdown. It has a number of singers making cameo appearances. It went to number 88 in Scotland. == References == Category:2020 songs Category:Kim Petras songs Category:Bubblegum pop songs Category:Disco songs Category:Funk songs
